<em>Bulletin of the Institute of Classical Studies</em>, (Supplement
<em>Philosophy, Science and Exegesis in Greek, Arabic and Latin
Commentaries</em>, Peter Adamson, H. Baltussen, Martin W. F. Stone
(eds)), 47(S83.2): 149&ndash;191.
doi:10.1111/j.2041&ndash;5370.2004.tb02314.x</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2004, &ldquo;One Aspect of the Avicennian
Turn in Sunn&#299; Theology&rdquo;, <em>Arabic Sciences and
Philosophy</em>, 14(1): 65&ndash;100.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2012a, &ldquo;Essence and Existence in the
Eleventh- and Twelfth-Century Islamic East
(<em>ma&scaron;riq</em>)&rdquo;, in Hasse and Bertolacci 2012:
27&ndash;50.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2012b, &ldquo;New Philosophical Texts of
Ya&#7717;y&#257; b. &#703;Ad&#299;: A Supplement to Endress&rsquo;
Analytical Inventory&rdquo;, in Opwis and Reisman 2012:
307&ndash;326.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2013, &ldquo;Avicenna&rsquo;s Islamic
Reception&rdquo;, in Adamson 2013a: 190&ndash;213.
doi:10.1017/CBO9781139047890.011</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2014, &ldquo;Towards a Genealogy of
Avicennism&rdquo;, <em>Oriens</em>, 42(3&ndash;4): 323&ndash;363.
doi:10.1163/18778372-04203003</li>

<li>Zarepour, Mohammad S., 2022, <em>Necessary Existence and
Monotheism: An Avicennian Account of the Islamic Conception of Divine
Unity</em>, Cambridge: Cambridge University Press.</li>

<li>Zamboni, Francesco Omar, 2023, <em>At the Roots of Causality.
Ontology and Aetiology from Avicenna to Fakhr al-D&#299;n
al-R&#257;z&#299;</em>, (Islamic philosophy, theology, and science,
124), Leiden: Brill.</li>

<li>Zimmermann, F.W., 1986, &ldquo;The Origins of the so-called
<em>Theology of Aristotle</em>&rdquo;, in <em>Pseudo-Aristotle in the
Middle Ages. The &lsquo;Theology&rsquo; and Other Texts</em>, Jill
Kraye, W.F. Ryan, and C.B. Schmitt (eds), London: Warburg Institute,
pp. 110&ndash;240.</li>

<li>Zonta, Mauro, 2001, &ldquo;Sulla tradizione ebraica di alcuni
commenti arabi alla <em>Metafisica</em> (Ab&#363;-l-Fara&#487;
ibn-al-&#7788;ayyib e Averro&egrave;)&rdquo;, <em>Documenti e Studi
sulla Tradizione Filosofica Medievale</em>, 12: 155&ndash;177.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2010, &ldquo;The revisions of Qalonymos ben
Qalonymos&rsquo; Hebrew translation of Averroes&rsquo; Middle
Commentary on the <em>Metaphysics</em>&rdquo;, <em>Documenti e Studi
sulla Tradizione Filosofica Medievale</em>, 21: 457&ndash;473.</li>
</ul>
</div> 

